AlphanumericConstant.vardesc: Constant numerical or text value to use in order to simplify runtime requirements since no processing needs to occur.

Constant.vardesc: Constant numerical or text value to use in order to simplify runtime requirements since no processing needs to occur.

dataMatrix.vardesc: DataMatrix object - table based element with value evaluated at run time based on row/col inputs (1-d or 2-d).

PublicVars.vardesc: Accessors of exposed properties of a component and its parent model object.

textField.vardesc: Text based sub-component value to store things like variable names, file paths, etc.

wsp_1tierflowby.varname: OM Water System Tiered Flow-By/Release Object
wsp_1tierflowby.vardesc: Contains a lookup table to calculate base flow-by/release, plus an if/else type condition to enable override, e.g. 10% of flow or MIF whichever is lower.

om_element_connection.vardesc: Link to OM modeling element in external database.  Provides access to run files, and enables paramterization to be passed to remote element.
